      "review_summary": "The PR adds opt-in reset-family transcript lookup to Gateway `chat.history` and `sessions_history`, updates Swift protocol generation/docs, and adds gateway, embedded-mode, tool, and prompt-snapshot coverage.\n\nPR surface: Source +279, Tests +247, Docs +6, Other +4. Total +536 across 28 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. at source level: current main has active-history plus same-session reset fallback but no family-history selector. The PR body and added tests demonstrate the intended reset-family path with on-disk fixtures, but this read-only review did not run a live channel reset scenario.",
